      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pump pressure rise — experimental comparison across speed range",
      "description": "Predicted pump pressure rise (ΔP) compared to bench-top measurements across rotational speeds from 2000 to 3500 rpm in 500 rpm increments. Maximum deviation is 4.1% at 3500 rpm. A structured uncertainty propagation was performed for epistemic uncertainty in fluid viscosity and geometry tolerances using a Monte Carlo approach with 500 samples.",
      "passFailStatus": "Pass",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/uq-03-pressure-rise-monte-carlo"
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/vr-04-flow-field-velocity-profiles",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Velocity profile comparison — impeller exit plane",
      "description": "Radial and tangential velocity profiles at the impeller exit plane compared against stereoscopic PIV measurements. RMS deviation is 6.3% of mean exit velocity. Uncertainty in PIV measurements due to seeding particle lag and laser sheet thickness is discussed qualitatively. No formal UQ artifact is linked; aleatory variability from pump-to-pump geometric variation in the experimental specimens is acknowledged but not formally propagated through the model.",
      "passFailStatus": "Pass"
    },
    {
